== Trivia == 
* Despite its age, as of 2026 the world has been kept alive continuously for over 3 years, which is ''over 1000 days''
* After the reception, popularity, and longevity of this world, Crazium would go on to make a world with the exact opposite concept: "[[Community:This Ship has 5 Years of Oxygen Remaining]]"
* For April Fool's day 2023, chess pieces were placed on the floor around the button. The timer was also inverted.

